name: arctic-viewer
description: Standalone application useful to load and explore cool data products.

packageJSON.name: arctic-viewer
packageJSON.description: Standalone application useful to load and explore in-situ/batch data products.

scripts.semantic-release: semantic-release pre && npm publish && semantic-release post
